        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>To improve the reliability of the heater or heater-A/C system in 2000, 5000, 8000 and 9000 Series
                    vehicles built before August 1, 1995, Navistar now offers a heavy duty blower motor. The heavy duty
                    motor is supplied with shaft bearings in place of sleeve bearings and longer brushes. The heavy duty
                    motor will mount in the same opening as the old style motor.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
